name: 李老师不是你老师
content: The video tells about the successful maiden flight of China's independently developed stratospheric airship "Dream Yuan" in 2015. It is also the world's first near-space airship flight with sustained power, controllable flight, and reusability. As an airship that can fly and operate in near-space, "Dream Yuan" has strong commercial and military uses. Therefore, its appearance will play an important role in promoting the development of China's near-space airships.
